gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Timberwolves 117, Knicks 100
gameRecap.excerpt: The Timberwolves defeated the Knicks, 117-100, Anthony Edwards recorded 23 points, 10 rebounds, and five assists for the Timberwolves, with Karl-Anthony Towns adding 20 points and five rebounds in the victory. Jalen Brunson added 25 points, six assists, and four rebounds for the Knicks in the losing effort. The Timberwolves improve to 10-3 in the regular season, while the Knicks fall to 8-6.
